Here's a PlantUML component diagram capturing the static architecture of the Pokemon game system, focusing on the general architectural concern:

```plantuml
@startuml Connor1996_Pokemon

package "Client" {
    [GUI Components] as GUI
    [Client Socket] as ClientSocket
    [Pokemon Factory] as PokemonFactory
    [ORM] as ClientORM
}

package "Server" {
    [Server Socket] as ServerSocket
    [Dispatcher] as Dispatcher
    [ORM] as ServerORM
    [Game Logic] as GameLogic
}

database "SQLite Database" as DB

[JSON Communication] as JSON

GUI --> ClientSocket : uses
GUI --> PokemonFactory : creates Pokemon
ClientSocket --> JSON : sends/receives
ServerSocket --> JSON : sends/receives
Dispatcher --> ServerSocket : handles requests
Dispatcher --> GameLogic : executes game actions
GameLogic --> ServerORM : persists data
ClientORM --> DB : reads/writes
ServerORM --> DB : reads/writes

@enduml
```